vite new tool for createing react app better than create-react-app
    npm create vite@latest ./ -- --template react  ---> 

install tailwindcss 
    npm install -D tailwindcss
    npx tailwindcss init        	

packages to use in portfolio 
    npm install 
        --legacy-peer-deps for instaling some packages compatible with older versions of react 
        @react-tree/fiber
        @react-tree/drei   those 2 for 3d animations 
        maath            for math functions to help with geomethery 
        react-tilt  for cool animations when hovering over the cards 
        react-vertical-timeline-component for timeline verical xd
        @emailjs/browser
        framer-motion
        react-router-dom
        \
        
run Vite with
    npm run dev
            